{"tid":2299240,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"東京一批蒙古族人向王毅抗議內蒙強推漢語教學","createTime":"2020-11-24T15:22:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-24T16:58:55.000Z","uid":133159,"like":23,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"b6f0b8f122893115ccc73852342d81a6e9c5e3d1","tid":2299240,"uid":133159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T15:22:55.000Z","msg":"在日本東京，50多名蒙古族人，趁中國外長王毅到訪，抗議内蒙古新學期加強推行漢語教學的政策。他們在國會議事堂外聚集，在王毅車隊進入附近的政府大樓後，於議事堂外圍舉起「停止壓迫蒙古人」、「撤回漢化教育」等標語和旗幟，不時高叫口號。現場數十名警員未有制止他們的行動。當地蒙古族人在9月曾經舉辦遊行，抗議中國當局推行有關政策。<br />\n<br />\n2020-11-24 22:34:03"},{"pid":"895677f999febfca850e6155e3b002511667673f","tid":2299240,"uid":89517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T15:23:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37da9e0834889927b73b29da2ca775ca8690d1b6","tid":2299240,"uid":138552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T15:24:27.000Z","msg":"日本好似都唔少蒙古人 最出名係啲相撲手"},{"pid":"5d84bc7cb2aa9b61cb1ed67183a5b89528498fd2","tid":2299240,"uid":8308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T15:24:45.000Z","msg":"蒙古人登報抗議！"},{"pid":"b2b510e3b4ae7f455a15eb693b51e0eaa10ca5ea","tid":2299240,"uid":70487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T15:25:06.000Z","msg":"境井仁<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24f6997102661daa84b3a244aebf6885560402ff","tid":2299240,"uid":282637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T16:58:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jUTaTWh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjUTaTWh.jpg&h=1414fc00&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}